{"tid":2118662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方向記協發信　要求處理6宗涉網媒投訴","createTime":"2020-07-21T14:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T16:05:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fec09fea6d01d6ccda7f8135dfa9667d6a9c0ed9","tid":2118662,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539111-20200721.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539111-20200721.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=69379c81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539111-20200721.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=340fae39\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539111-20200721.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓，昨日向記者協會發信，要求處理6宗「不實或有違操守報道」投訴，涉及6間網上媒體，指控包括涉嫌派出未成年學生記者、向女警外觀發出冒犯評論、近距離拍攝警員容貌或印有警員個人資料的單張等。<br />\n<br />\n記協回信說，以警方身分投訴不屬公眾投訴範疇，6宗投訴大部分涉及記者個別行為舉止，並非「不實或有違操守報道」，但基於記協是專業的新聞工作組織，決定調查投訴個案，要求警方盡快提供相關報道原文、事件詳情、在場警員聯絡方法，以便跟進。<br />\n<br />\n其中，就有網媒派未成年學生記者，警方批評媒體罔顧記者人身安全。記協則質疑，學生記者該時處於大型商場，警方如何預知現場環境危險。<br />\n<br />\n警方又批評有媒體以「市民合力擊退落單警」為題，批評襲警的並非一般「市民」，而是罪犯。記協認為，沒有當場被捕、未被法庭定罪人士，記者難以判斷他們是否罪犯，亦質疑成為罪犯是否代表失去市民身分。"},{"pid":"c062b7cea7dbfefd691b498d02f797277fa9a3de","tid":2118662,"uid":244876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如直接成立狗記<br />\n強制市民剩係睇狗講既野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a4642bbc592a243d3167d1e5b2fd4d86c1501b","tid":2118662,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c062b7cea7dbfefd691b498d02f797277fa9a3de","tid":2118662,"uid":244876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如直接成立狗記<br />\n強制市民剩係睇狗講既野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"佢地想嫁<br />\n你唔好話"},{"pid":"bf3083ad170dba39b2b7fbe806937a9a4c7a5b7a","tid":2118662,"uid":229369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a91ef86841c393f1852e4871b37ba724b0b680a4","tid":2118662,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:03:03.000Z","msg":"同佢講適當時候會處理咪得，用番佢地d語言"},{"pid":"baad7b56c48850e20b3cfdc2108a272fac4fa7bc","tid":2118662,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8a4642bbc592a243d3167d1e5b2fd4d86c1501b","tid":211